just_use board_geometry.go

# label: ELEGANT
# role: encodes domain knowledge

Owns where on the play surface stacks can live. CardHeight and CardPitch
are co-located with overlap/bounds logic (mirrors elm-lynrummy's
BoardGeometry.elm placement); changing pitch here is a single-file edit.

The referee calls checkGeometry to reject moves whose result would push a
stack off-board or overlap another stack. Default bounds (800×600, 5-unit
margin) live in events.go where CheckEvent invokes the referee.
